replies.body:
That makes so much sense-it's probably too late to swap it over to where the snowballs don't require that limit right?

Because I've tried just gifting people snowballs really quickly several times now hopelessly. At first I tried the gifting button in the post-game lobby, but that didn't work so I did the process of friending them, going to the gifting section, and going to the snowball icons... To find out that they already had all the icons.

Should've known something was up when it did this repeatedly.

I was just trying to spread the festive spirit around with some cheap 100 IP icons to random folk. {{summoner:3}} 

Snowballs: For when honor isn't enough, but you ain't dropping RP on that random person. {{summoner:31}}
